{"tid":973931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"炸開的胸部！23歲網美愛秀「竹竿腰西瓜奶」網一面倒批：實在不好看","createTime":"2019-01-08T13:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T01:13:50.000Z","uid":212399,"like":23,"dislike":584,"uniUserReply":112,"replies":[{"pid":"d4d461e927870cc165349cdd0e7d2a41cc921f19","tid":973931,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:33:07.000Z","msg":"文／紅豆Q粉粿<br />\n許多女孩渴望擁有巨乳、S形曲線，希望藉此吸引異性目光，然而身材比例過了頭，未必獲得好評！<br />\n南韓一位23歲的網美，名為Lee Seo Young，她是IG、臉書、twitter上的大紅人，因為她有著驚人比例的「竹竿腰」和「西瓜奶」，然而，她卻沒有獲得眾多好評和讚賞，許多網友（包含男性）都留言批評她，「比例實在太怪了！」「好像外星人！」「老實告訴你，真的不好看。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3810/3810639.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3810%2F3810639.jpg&h=cb91b612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我們來細看Lee Seo Young的照片，她的每一張照片，都讓人目不轉睛，那張擁有精緻五官的臉蛋，鼻梁直挺、額頭臉頰膨膨的、下巴尖、眼睛超大，相當精緻。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3810/3810641.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3810%2F3810641.jpg&h=7c15c06e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3810/3810643.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3810%2F3810643.jpg&h=3e30c713&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再來是她的身材，不僅四肢纖長，腰部瘦的像手掌就能輕易握住，胸圍、臀圍卻相反地很豐滿、圓潤。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3810/3810638.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3810%2F3810638.jpg&h=073bb68c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3810/3810644.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3810%2F3810644.jpg&h=34f5ce0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3810/3810642.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3810%2F3810642.jpg&h=f29ac78d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLee Seo Young深受取多廠商青睞、業配接不完，然而許多粉絲都認為她整過頭、已經不符合正常人類的身型比例。<br />\n各位怎麼看呢？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/40836\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F40836&d=YzhzPCpgBYRVwF9Kd3lPzi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=d940eff2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/40836</a>"},{"pid":"97e544ddd65d0c18344cd6cdb6a21b94fbd454df","tid":973931,"uid":33907,"like":830,"dislike":17,"score":813,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:34:24.000Z","msg":"超級唔好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比例好差 睇到唔舒服"},{"pid":"e32ae82a4d00986ed594ef76ff6b35010a9de42f","tid":973931,"uid":18638,"like":24,"dislike":95,"score":-71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:35:10.000Z","msg":"好睇！"},{"pid":"20949e48f0d529b25a242c29c3ac682410def880","tid":973931,"uid":194281,"like":294,"dislike":5,"score":289,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:36:09.000Z","msg":"老左就知味道"},{"pid":"10bd7931c16a43dc0b843a5de37611da02da5654","tid":973931,"uid":211579,"like":323,"dislike":3,"score":320,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:37:11.000Z","msg":"想嘔，塊面整到冇一寸皮膚係自然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98319ba779c6c3e3fec220793d993dcb53bfce09","tid":973931,"uid":212399,"like":229,"dislike":9,"score":220,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRRSmnZNAuCi4wqnNtO6boLLbAY-nVcdc4-fGaVuSt9XEtVsI6j\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcRRSmnZNAuCi4wqnNtO6boLLbAY-nVcdc4-fGaVuSt9XEtVsI6j&h=e82452e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77d5160b5496b4dce0d65ee858ef00cb84a729ae","tid":973931,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T13:38:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7722738334f8428cf0ec7ae07bbe391019daab7","tid":973931,"uid":18569,"like":57